title: FULL SHOW: The Breakfast Club Talks With John Boyega, Symba, NLE Choppa's Public Breakup
itunes:title: FULL SHOW: The Breakfast Club Talks With John Boyega, Symba, NLE Choppa's Public Breakup
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we are joined by Symba who came to talk about his new album. We also are joined by John Boyega who came to talk about the new film "Woman King". Later we talk about NLE Choppa's public breakup with his girlfriend during the rumor report. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
